2015-01-14 Release 0.4.0
- Raise file descriptor limit for Heka daemon.
- Restart (rather than reload) on upstart config changes.
- Add header to config files that are managed by Puppet.

2014-12-16 Release 0.3.0
- Add `encoder_options` and `output_options` params to
  `heka::plugin::elasticsearch`.

2014-12-12 Release 0.2.0
- Add `protocol` param to `heka::plugin::graphite`.

2014-12-08 Release 0.1.0
- Add `package_ensure` param.
- Add `service_ensure` param.

2014-12-05 Release 0.0.1
- Initial release.
- Manage package/config/service.
- Manage a handful of generic plugins.
